metadata.name: The Warrior - Mark of Bravery
metadata.description:
The warriors who save communities,
countries, nations, land, culture, lives,
and your freedom at the cost of their
lives.
The concept of valour is as old as
life on earth and still exists in many
new forms with new rules, but we can
still witness the first nation warriors
on the land of Africa. and who
knows when they will have to face an
unknown one in the future?
